{"tid":1015364,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【可樂迷留意】 可口可樂10年來首推橙味雲呢拿新口味","createTime":"2019-02-10T02:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T03:38:22.000Z","uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f0f6282ec3fd017706ed0a1b2d91e4a945df72ef","tid":1015364,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:33:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cms.exmoo.com/uploads/2019-02-09/QI0Z4iuhn9b5OenY1ZO8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.exmoo.com%2Fuploads%2F2019-02-09%2FQI0Z4iuhn9b5OenY1ZO8.jpg&h=d0fd728c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可口可樂公司近日宣布，將推出橙味雲呢拿可樂<br />\n（Orange Vanilla Coke）及橙味雲呢拿無糖可樂（Orange Vanilla Coke Zero Sugar），於本月25日在全美國發售，是相隔10年來再有新口味登場。<br />\n<br />\n可口可樂公司曾於1985年及2007年推出過其他口味，如櫻桃味可樂（Cherry Coke）和雲呢拿可樂（Vanilla Coke）。可口可樂總監Kate Carpenter表示，這兩種口味及無糖版本銷情增長良好，所以公司決定再研發新口味。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，兩款新可樂已在加拿大測試，其味道仿似橙味夾心雪條「Creamsicle」，十分易入口。<br />\n<br />\n可口可樂官方網站暫時未有關於本澳發售新口味可樂的消息。"},{"pid":"bfadf6548cc1a39982fa0e8dcf85a8645230353e","tid":1015364,"uid":9231,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:35:24.000Z","msg":"我要原味雲尼拿呀屌"},{"pid":"f866f93689dad14988e48afd4f44714bf814528a","tid":1015364,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0f6282ec3fd017706ed0a1b2d91e4a945df72ef","tid":1015364,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:33:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cms.exmoo.com/uploads/2019-02-09/QI0Z4iuhn9b5OenY1ZO8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.exmoo.com%2Fuploads%2F2019-02-09%2FQI0Z4iuhn9b5OenY1ZO8.jpg&h=d0fd728c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可口可樂公司近日宣布，將推出橙味雲呢拿可樂<br />\n（Orange Vanilla Coke）及橙味雲呢拿無糖可樂（Orange Vanilla Coke Zero Sugar），於本月25日在全美國發售，是相隔10年來再有新口味登場。<br />\n<br />\n可口可樂公司曾於1985年及2007年推出過其他口味，如櫻桃味可樂（Cherry Coke）和雲呢拿可樂（Vanilla Coke）。可口可樂總監Kate Carpenter表示，這兩種口味及無糖版本銷情增長良好，所以公司決定再研發新口味。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，兩款新可樂已在加拿大測試，其味道仿似橙味夾心雪條「Creamsicle」，十分易入口。<br />\n<br />\n可口可樂官方網站暫時未有關於本澳發售新口味可樂的消息。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:39:31.000Z","msg":"兩款新可樂已在加拿大測試<br />\n<br />\n都唔見有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a723bc8c20ed9e410fe80657089337b6d83c9a3e","tid":1015364,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T03:35:08.000Z","msg":"櫻桃味可樂 --&gt; 飲有汽咳藥水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a103a16faa45269bb2ad1b4b482f8726c47112ac","tid":1015364,"uid":175865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T03:38:22.000Z","msg":"芬達溝可樂啊？"}]}